  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 7</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You must be in a Jyuuken stance to use this technique. You make 4 Jyuuken attacks against the target, at your highest attack bonus. These attacks cannot score a critical hit and deal only half damage, but each hit deals an additional 1 point of Chakra damage, as well as 16 tenketsu damage. A creature's Chakra Pool cannot be reduced below 1 due to this damage. The target is @Condition[dazed;duration=1]{dazed} for 1 round (Fortitude negates).<br><br>Each additional time this technique or Hyuuga Ryuu: Ougi - Hakke Hyakunijuuhachi Shou is used against the same creature within a 24 hour period reduces the tenketsu damage per hit by 4.</p>\n\n\n\n",
